Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.48,0:00:08.46,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}キルア あんたのおかげよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.48,0:00:08.46,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Fearsome monsters... Exotic creatures...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.97,0:00:12.95,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}起きてから　ずっと　そうだった。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.97,0:00:12.95,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Vast riches... Hidden treasures...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.95,0:00:16.95,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}自分が無力だなんて思わないで。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.95,0:00:16.95,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Evil enclaves... Unexplored lands...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.58,0:00:23.46,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}私がゴンのため
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.58,0:00:23.46,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The word "unknown" holds magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.46,0:00:26.46,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}何かできるなら喜んでする。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.46,0:00:26.46,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}And some incredible people are \Ndrawn to that magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.97,0:00:30.47,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}でも　忘れないで。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.97,0:00:30.47,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}They are known...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.99,0:00:36.99,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ゴンに 一番必要なのは　あなたなのよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.99,0:00:36.99,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}...as Hunters!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.93,0:02:14.42,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ゴンを思うキルアの言葉が
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.93,0:02:14.42,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Reply x From x Dad
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.42,0:02:18.92,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}奇跡的に パームを元の姿に戻した
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.42,0:02:18.92,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The box that had been sealed with Nen
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.96,0:02:26.93,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}その頃　西塔の２階では メレオロンの 再三の制止を振り切り
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.96,0:02:26.93,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}contained three mysterious items. One of them, an old cassette tape, gave Gon his first chance
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.93,0:02:30.43,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}プフとの 直接対決に臨んだナックルが
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.93,0:02:30.43,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}to hear his father's voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.43,0:02:34.43,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}彼らの前に姿を現していた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.43,0:02:34.43,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yo, Gon...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.94,0:02:39.93,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}プフ。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.94,0:02:39.93,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}This is my dad's voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.44,0:02:53.94,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}表　出ろや。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.44,0:02:53.94,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If you do, keep on listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.45,0:03:07.95,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ですが　その前に まず言っておきましょう。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.45,0:03:07.95,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm guessing that's a "yes."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.92,0:03:13.43,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ここにいる私は　いわば分身。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.92,0:03:13.43,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Then I'll ask you once more. Are you prepared?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.43,0:03:18.45,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}本体は　すでに 王の元へと向かっています。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.43,0:03:18.45,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Hunters are selfish creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.99,0:03:31.43,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}自身が　煙の檻から脱出した後
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.99,0:03:31.43,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If you're only slightly interested in seeing me, you should stop the tape now. I'll give you a minute to consider it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.43,0:03:33.93,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ナックルとモラウが 接触していることを
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.43,0:03:33.93,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.96,0:03:49.53,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}分身のことは　ボスから聞いてる。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.96,0:03:49.53,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I guess you really do want to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.53,0:03:52.03,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}事実だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.53,0:03:52.03,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But I don't want to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.45,0:03:59.42,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ナックルが口にしたのは ゴンに伝えるためである
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.45,0:03:59.42,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I don't know how I could face you now. After all, I chose my own desires
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.42,0:04:01.94,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}先に真実を述べることで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.42,0:04:01.94,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}over my parental duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.94,0:04:05.43,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}心理的に先手を打つ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.94,0:04:05.43,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm a bad person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.50,0:04:18.92,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}だが　なぜ自分から言い出す？ プフの目的は　ユピーにあった
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.50,0:04:18.92,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm guessing that by the time \Nyou hear this tape, at least ten years will have passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.92,0:04:24.93,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ナックルが　ここにいる以上 ユピーは 彼を見逃したことになり
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.92,0:04:24.93,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But one thing still hasn't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.97,0:04:32.97,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}理由によっては…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.97,0:04:32.97,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm still me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.97,0:04:54.93,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}プフは ユピーに感じた変化の真意を
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.97,0:04:54.93,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}As you listen to this tape, I'm off doing reckless things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.93,0:04:56.93,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ナックルから探るため
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.93,0:04:56.93,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If you want to see me, find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.93,0:05:01.95,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}この場を 穏便に離れる必要があったのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.93,0:05:01.95,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But as I said before, I don't want to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.95,0:05:05.94,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}まず　彼を納得させるため。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.95,0:05:05.94,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If I sense you nearby, \NI'll make myself scarce.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.94,0:05:10.98,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}彼は　私がこの場から動かないよう 要求しています。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.94,0:05:10.98,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Catch me if you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.98,0:05:14.93,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}１対１の勝負なら 場所を変えるため
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.98,0:05:14.93,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You are a Hunter, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.95,0:05:22.44,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}私は分身。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.95,0:05:22.44,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Your dad isn't gonna be easy to track.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.44,0:05:24.92,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}鱗粉も使いません。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.44,0:05:24.92,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Oh, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:29.46,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それでもよろしければ お相手します。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:29.46,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Ging's still there. Oh, I forgot to mention something...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.03,0:05:36.42,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それ故の告白です。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.03,0:05:36.42,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It's about your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.42,0:05:39.92,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}背後から　わざわざ声を掛け
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.42,0:05:39.92,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If you want to know more, keep listening. If you're not interested...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.92,0:05:42.93,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}１対１の戦いを望む人間には
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.92,0:05:42.93,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.93,0:05:49.41,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}正直に話していると 見せることが効果的だと プフは知っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.93,0:05:49.41,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yeah. But he might have left you a clue. I doubt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.49,0:05:55.49,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ウソをつけ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.49,0:05:55.49,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Besides, I already told you... My mom is Mito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.42,0:06:02.42,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}お前は　さっき 俺を後ろから殺そうとした。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.42,0:06:02.42,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.43,0:06:08.43,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}自分でも　そう言った。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.43,0:06:08.43,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Are you hungry? I'll go grab something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.43,0:06:10.92,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ナックル　だまされるな。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.43,0:06:10.92,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.47,0:06:17.94,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}まず お前が本体でなく分身だって？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.47,0:06:17.94,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Hey, Gon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.94,0:06:20.43,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}その証拠が　どこにある？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.94,0:06:20.43,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The tape started moving all by itself! What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.43,0:06:22.45,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}くっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.43,0:06:22.45,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}There's aura around the tape player!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.45,0:06:24.42,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}確かに
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.45,0:06:24.42,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It's Nen... \NNen is rewinding the cassette!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.96,0:06:35.96,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}こいつ　厄介だ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.96,0:06:35.96,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}No, he infused this player with \NNen over ten years ago! So it would start rewinding, \Nonce it was stopped! Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.45,0:06:40.45,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}恐らく　敵の中で一番
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.45,0:06:40.45,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.45,0:06:44.45,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}こいつが 揺るがぬ意志を持っている
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.45,0:06:44.45,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Now it's recording! I get it! He's erasing his message!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.44,0:06:50.94,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}彼が　ピトーと共に 縛られている現状は
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.44,0:06:50.94,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}What? It's not working! I can't stop it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.94,0:06:55.01,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}むしろ 歓迎すべきなのかもしれません
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.94,0:06:55.01,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.01,0:06:57.42,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}なぜなら彼は
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.01,0:06:57.42,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It still won't stop! I pulled the plug!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.42,0:07:01.42,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}揺るがぬ意志で　ここにいるから
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.42,0:07:01.42,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Sorry, Gon. I'll have to break it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.42,0:07:13.98,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}私が本体かどうかを 証明するのは 私自身をすこぶる不利にするので 言えませんね。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.42,0:07:13.98,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Damn! No good! There's Nen protecting the player!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.44,0:07:29.95,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}この後　どうするかは あなたにお任せします。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.44,0:07:29.95,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It's finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.94,0:07:40.93,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}やめろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.94,0:07:40.93,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Now it's recording! I get it! He's erasing his message!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.97,0:07:56.01,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ハハハハ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.97,0:07:56.01,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm guessing he didn't want to leave any clues.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.01,0:07:58.44,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}アハハハ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.01,0:07:58.44,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Clues?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.44,0:08:01.93,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}アハハハ…！　ハハハハ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.44,0:08:01.93,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You can extract a lot of information \Nfrom an audio clip. Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.93,0:08:10.44,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ハハハハ…！ アハハハ…！　ハハハハ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.93,0:08:10.44,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You can determine the \Nspeaker's height, weight, gender, age, facial features, chronic diseases, and state of mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.44,0:08:14.01,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}アハハハ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.44,0:08:14.01,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}From the background noise, \Nyou can also determine the location.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.53,0:08:20.03,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}来るか来ないかは　あなた次第！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.53,0:08:20.03,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But he was more worried \Nabout something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.45,0:08:24.42,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}くっ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.45,0:08:24.42,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Nen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.94,0:08:32.94,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}プフのことは謝る！ 僕がいればいいだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.94,0:08:32.94,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I wouldn't be surprised if \Nthere were a Nen user somewhere who could analyze \Ndata better than a machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.02,0:08:39.44,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}１０分。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.02,0:08:39.44,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Oh, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.44,0:08:46.44,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}えっ？ 予定より１０分早く　治せ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.44,0:08:46.44,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Your dad's a tough nut. Since the tape's useless now, we only have two clues left...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.93,0:08:54.97,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ピトーは　戦慄していた
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.93,0:08:54.97,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The ring and the memory card.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.97,0:08:58.02,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}この場が どうなろうと構わないと
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.97,0:08:58.02,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I doubt the ring will help, but the memory card could be important.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.02,0:09:02.94,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}プフが判断し　離れたことにも 少なからず動揺したが
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.02,0:09:02.94,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yeah, it's smaller than a normal memory card. Maybe you need a special machine to use it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.94,0:09:07.45,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それ以上に プフの挑発を意に介さず
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.94,0:09:07.45,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Huh? You can't tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.45,0:09:11.95,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}時間の短縮を告げた ゴンを恐れた
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.45,0:09:11.95,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}This memory card only works with the JS. The JS? A gaming console called the JoyStation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.94,0:09:19.94,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}((時間は？ どれだけ待てばいい？))
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.94,0:09:19.94,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You don't know anything, do you? If this island still has tape players, \Nit probably has a console.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.94,0:09:24.43,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}((完全に回復させるには
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.94,0:09:24.43,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Is there a toy store here? Yeah, there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.43,0:09:27.43,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}３４時間は　かかると思う))
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.43,0:09:27.43,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Okay, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.94,0:09:34.96,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}((１時間あれば…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.94,0:09:34.96,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Oh, where are you going? The toy store.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.96,0:09:38.93,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}重大な危機を 乗り切れるところまでは治せる))
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.96,0:09:38.93,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It's outside the port! Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.93,0:09:44.43,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}当初　コムギを守り 完治させたい一心から
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.93,0:09:44.43,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Have a safe trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.46,0:09:58.03,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}実は ピトーがコムギの状態を見て
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.46,0:09:58.03,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}So this is a JoyStation...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.03,0:10:01.93,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}完治にかかると 踏んだ時間だった
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.03,0:10:01.93,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}This brings back memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.93,0:10:05.92,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}しかし　幾度かの経験で
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.93,0:10:05.92,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I used to play with these all the time. There were a bunch of hidden \Ngems for this console.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.92,0:10:10.43,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「ドクターブライス」の技術は 成長していた
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.92,0:10:10.43,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Then is this memory card \None of those hidden gems?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.43,0:10:15.43,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}治療しながら　１０分は 早められるかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.43,0:10:15.43,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I don't see a title anywhere. You've never played any video games, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.43,0:10:19.00,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そう思っていた矢先であった
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.43,0:10:19.00,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That's unusual. Really? That isn't a game disc.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.00,0:10:21.44,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}偶然かもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.00,0:10:21.44,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It holds a game's memory data.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.44,0:10:23.92,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}プフの去り際のセリフに
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.44,0:10:23.92,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}So you can't use it to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.92,0:10:28.43,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ゴンが同調しただけの 可能性が高い
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.92,0:10:28.43,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yeah, you're supposed to \Nput the disc in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.43,0:10:38.50,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そう思いながら　ピトーは 不吉な思いを振り払えずにいた 命懸けになる
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.43,0:10:38.50,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But if you insert the memory card and \Npower it on without a game inside, you can see which games are using that memory. Oh, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.50,0:10:41.44,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}でないと　こいつの牙は…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.50,0:10:41.44,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It looks like there's only one game saved on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.93,0:10:47.93,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}王の喉元にも 届き得るかもしれない！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.93,0:10:47.93,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It's called Greed Island. Greed Island?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.92,0:10:52.42,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}分かった。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.92,0:10:52.42,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Anyway, there are a bunch of saves.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.92,0:10:55.97,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ナックル。 おっ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.92,0:10:55.97,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I doubt it will do any good, \Nbut I'll copy the data just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.97,0:11:01.43,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ここは　俺１人で大丈夫。 さっきは　ああ言ったけど
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.97,0:11:01.43,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Copying Greed Island. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.43,0:11:05.45,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}プフの本体が王の所へ 向かったっていうのは
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.43,0:11:05.45,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.45,0:11:07.45,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}本当だと思う。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.45,0:11:07.45,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Searching on-line.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.92,0:11:12.44,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}南だよ　王は。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.92,0:11:12.44,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We know the game's name. So I'm looking for a store that sells it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.51,0:11:24.95,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ゴンは　キルアと共に その現場に居合わせた
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.51,0:11:24.95,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}There aren't any used copies... An out-of-print game would still have \Nsome used copies floating around.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.95,0:11:28.42,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それを知らないピトーが プフとのたくらみを
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.95,0:11:28.42,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It's possible that this game isn't for sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.42,0:11:31.42,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}看破されていたのだと 判断したのは
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.42,0:11:31.42,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}What do you mean? It could be an indie game
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.42,0:11:39.98,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}思考の流れとして当然であった もうろうとした恐れが 確信に変わった瞬間である
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.42,0:11:39.98,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}that was never for sale or was \Nbanned for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.98,0:11:45.44,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ピトーは 自らの使命を完全に覚悟した
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.98,0:11:45.44,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Anyway, I'll keep searching. There we go. This game was sold through \Nlegitimate channels.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.48,0:11:58.43,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}殺さねばならない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.48,0:11:58.43,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}And what's with that price tag?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.43,0:12:00.95,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}何としても
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.43,0:12:00.95,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Five hundred, eighty million?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.95,0:12:02.92,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}こいつを
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.95,0:12:02.92,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It's five billion, eight hundred million! Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.92,0:12:06.44,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}王のために！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.92,0:12:06.44,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That's ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.44,0:12:13.94,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}いや　ダメだ 彼女を危険にさらせない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.44,0:12:13.94,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That isn't very many. It's practically nothing! The developers were cocky... The number is way too low!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.50,0:12:19.94,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}まず 治した彼女を誰に任せる？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.50,0:12:19.94,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But it makes sense. The price is ridiculous, \Nbut Hunters can afford it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.94,0:12:24.94,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}プフもユピーも コムギを煙たがっている
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.94,0:12:24.94,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That explains how they sold out. Do the makers have any left in stock?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.94,0:12:26.93,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ダメだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.94,0:12:26.93,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yeah, I guess we could ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.93,0:12:31.93,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}僕がいなくなったら 誰がコムギを王へ？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.93,0:12:31.93,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The game you are inquiring about \Nis no longer in stock.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.44,0:12:38.54,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ゴン。 おめぇの言いたいことは理解した。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.44,0:12:38.54,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Unfortunately, there are no plans \Nto print additional copies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.54,0:12:43.04,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}その上で　俺は俺のやり方でやる。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.54,0:12:43.04,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I see, thanks. That's a no-go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.93,0:12:48.95,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ユピーは…。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.93,0:12:48.95,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I guess we'll have to find someone with \Na copy and ask them to let us have it. Yeah, our best bet is to advertise \Non a reverse auction website
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.94,0:13:01.50,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}いや　何でもねえ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.94,0:13:01.50,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If we pool our money from the arena, that's eight hundred million.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.50,0:13:06.92,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}自らの情報で ゴンに動揺や迷いが生じたら
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.50,0:13:06.92,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Then we need another five billion... Not necessarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.92,0:13:13.44,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それが結果　死を招くこともある じゃあな。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.92,0:13:13.44,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Huh? With these private deals, \Nthe seller holds all the power. Typically, they'll ask for more \Nthan the original price.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:19.94,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}辛うじて ナックルは思いとどまった
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:19.94,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}So it'll cost even more? Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.95,0:13:38.95,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}なぜ　貴様が 余の名前を知っている？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.95,0:13:38.95,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Price negotiable."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.03,0:13:49.53,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}部下が　お主の 母親の臨終に立ち会ったのよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.03,0:13:49.53,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.97,0:13:55.47,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}いまわの言葉が お主の名だったそうだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.97,0:13:55.47,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We already have over ten thousand hits! So that's it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.47,0:14:01.47,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}その部下も護衛軍との戦闘で 死んでしまったかもな。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.47,0:14:01.47,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}They're trying to foist counterfeits off on us. That should have been obvious, \Nconsidering the price. This plan is a wash.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.53,0:14:10.53,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}やる気になったかね？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.53,0:14:10.53,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Besides, we can't even tell \Nif it's the real game.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.47,0:14:16.94,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}わしに負けを 認めさすことができれば
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.47,0:14:16.94,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If we dig more deeply on-line, \Nwe might uncover more information.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.94,0:14:19.94,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}教えてやらんでもないぞ？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.94,0:14:19.94,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But I'm not too familiar with that stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.47,0:14:27.47,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}殺さず　気の済むまでか…。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.47,0:14:27.47,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Is there anyone who knows a bunch \Nabout games and the Net? Oh, there's someone who \Nknows a lot about both.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.56,0:14:35.06,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「飛車角落ち」 といったところだな。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.56,0:14:35.06,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He might even own a copy of Greed Island. What? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.95,0:14:47.95,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}まぁ　すぐに詰んでやろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.95,0:14:47.95,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Gotoh-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.46,0:15:05.98,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}王が応じると同時
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.46,0:15:05.98,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}What? Killua wants to talk to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.98,0:15:08.46,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ネテロは飛んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.98,0:15:08.46,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Screw that! Tell him I'm not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.98,0:15:44.48,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}いつからだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.98,0:15:44.48,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm busy here. Greed Island ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.45,0:15:52.95,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}敵の攻撃を 待つようになったのは
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.45,0:15:52.95,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I never expected you to ask me \Nabout a super-rare game. You don't own a copy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.98,0:15:58.95,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}) )
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.98,0:15:58.95,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}No, I don't. I wanted one, but I was five \Nwhen the game went on sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.95,0:16:00.95,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13})
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.95,0:16:00.95,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}So I didn't have any money.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.07,0:16:05.62,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13})
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.07,0:16:05.62,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}There were over twenty thousand \Nrequests for a hundred copies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.62,0:16:08.62,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13})
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.62,0:16:08.62,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Even though each copy cost five billion, \Neight hundred million Jenny in cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.46,0:16:21.47,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13})
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.46,0:16:21.47,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I tried looking around later, but I couldn't even find an owner. It's a legendary game for all kinds of reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.97,0:16:29.47,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13})
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.97,0:16:29.47,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It's impossible. Forget it. Even I had to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.06,0:16:32.98,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13})
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.06,0:16:32.98,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Oh? You gave up because it was \Nbeyond your ability?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.97,0:17:46.47,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}一体　いつからだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.97,0:17:46.47,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Sorry. I ended up trading the copy \Nof the memory card.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.45,0:17:59.53,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}差し出して来る両の手に
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.45,0:17:59.53,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}First, there's a website for Hunters, only accessible by Hunters.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.53,0:18:04.53,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}間を置かずに 応えられるようになったのは
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.53,0:18:04.53,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We can probably find leads \Non Greed Island there. Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.46,0:18:08.94,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そんなんじゃねえだろ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.46,0:18:08.94,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'll have to use my Hunter License. Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.94,0:18:12.44,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺が求めた武の極みは!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.94,0:18:12.44,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If you use your home computer, \Nthey'll know your address! You'll have bad guys who want your \Nlicense showing up on the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.94,0:18:32.95,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}敗色濃い難敵にこそ 全霊をもって臨むこと!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.94,0:18:32.95,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Well, I still don't know the address. My brother promised to tell me, \Nonce he's received the memory card. The second lead is the auction \Nin Yorknew City.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.45,0:19:57.95,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ここは墓場。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.45,0:19:57.95,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm going to end this legend...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.96,0:20:04.96,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}貴様のな。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.96,0:20:04.96,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Wow... There's so much food!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.45,0:21:34.95,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}感謝するぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.45,0:21:34.95,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Ging told Gon to find him, \Nleaving behind a riddle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.04,0:21:48.95,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}お前と出会えた これまでの全てに！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.04,0:21:48.95,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}In order to solve that riddle \Nand meet his father, Gon leaves his home again and heads \Nto Yorknew City with Killua.
